==2007 Cricket World Cup== {{Main article|2007 Cricket World Cup}}
Bermuda qualified for their first Cricket World Cup in 2007, and were drawn against hosts Bangladesh, India and Sri Lanka. They lost all three matches, and failed to qualify for the Knockout stage.<ref name="CWC2007"/>
