{{Infobox country at games | NOC = KOR | NOCname = [[Korean Olympic Committee]] | oldcode = | year = 2005 | date = | games = East Asian Games | location = [[Macau]] | competitors = 302 | sports = 16 | flagbearer = | officials = 95 | gold = 32 | silver = 48 | bronze = 65 | rank = 3 | appearances = auto | seealso = | website = }}
'''South Korea''' competed at the '''[[2005 East Asian Games|2005]] [[East Asian Games]]''' held in [[Macao, China]] from October 29, 2005 to November 6, 2005. South Korea finished third with 32 gold medals, 48 silver medals, and 65 bronze medals.
