'''Zgharta Sports Complex - Mirdachiyyé Stadium''' is a 5,000 capacity use [[stadium]] in [[Zgharta]], [[Lebanon]].  It is currently used for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Salam Zgharta]] and some others clubs of divisions 3 and 4 of the city [[Zgharta]].

